{"tid":1846664,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"藍絲，親中，愛国嘅各位，你地開始後悔無支持抗爭者未？","createTime":"2020-01-27T16:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-02T02:38:02.000Z","uid":1477,"like":68,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"91f69d670daf73d3ef8c1df2ec72ecdb582d8631","tid":1846664,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:48:48.000Z","msg":"話左政府仆街<br />\n你唔信<br />\n<br />\n話左中共仆街<br />\n你唔信<br />\n<br />\n話左香港警察仆街<br />\n你唔信<br />\n<br />\n而家一車車中国人車落黎香港<br />\n成班超級帶菌者陀衰家<br />\n<br />\n而家政府打死唔封關<br />\n遲早一齊陷港鏟<br />\n<br />\n而家醫護唔罷工<br />\n都遲早比班中国人累撚死<br />\n咁香港人就真係玩撚完<br />\n<br />\n而家入境處拒絕比湖北人入境<br />\n黑警放人入黎香港<br />\n<br />\n香港九成九玩撚完架喇<br />\n<br />\n不過唔係死係廢青暴徒手上<br />\n<br />\n而係死係中共手上<br />\n而你地班廢柴藍絲就係佢地嘅最大支持者<br />\n你地藍絲就係最大幫凶<br />\n<br />\n我就無所謂架<br />\n我地目標不嬲係攬炒<br />\n攬住你地班藍絲一齊死都幾過癮<br />\n<br />\n同埋我地都盡左力<br />\n反抗唔到咪死囉<br />\n都預左<br />\n我想落去見手足好耐<br />\n<br />\n不過你地就慘喇<br />\n奶得咁辛苦都係要一齊死<br />\n<br />\n邊個叫你地唔支持香港獨立？<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立，唯一出路。<br />\n驅逐共匪，光復香港。"},{"pid":"e061e92e4d02c99f4c26db55074827632a26c199","tid":1846664,"uid":117235,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0OX34y3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0OX34y3.jpg&h=d930b64f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WNPfFJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2WNPfFJ.jpg&h=033f6cbd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"908412bb475888bf4e9645625598f00bf65c520e","tid":1846664,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e061e92e4d02c99f4c26db55074827632a26c199","tid":1846664,"uid":117235,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T16:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0OX34y3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0OX34y3.jpg&h=d930b64f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2WNPfFJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/